<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Comment on {$post->getTitle()}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
        .notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .button {
                display: block;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Verify Your Comment</h1>
        </div>

        <p>Hello, {$comment->getAuthorName()}</p>

        <p>Thank you! You recently commented on "<strong>{$post->getTitle()}</strong>" and we need to verify your email address.</p>

        <p>Please click the button below to verify your comment:</p>

        <p>
            <a href="{$verificationUrl}" class="button">Verify Your Comment</a>
        </p>

        <p class="notice">This link expires in {$expiresInDays} days. If you did not leave this comment, please ignore this email.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>{$siteName}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
